Class VeeplayCastConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.veeplay.cast.VeeplayCastConfiguration

  • public class VeeplayCastConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Andrei on 18.02.2016. Class for encapsulating Chromecast playback configuration data, such as the look of the persistent notification shown during cast playback.
